ðŸ“Š Dataset Schema (Entities & Attributes)
| Column Name       | Description                                |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| `campaign_id`     | Unique ID of email campaign                |
| `campaign_name`   | Campaign type (Diwali Sale, Welcome, etc.) |
| `customer_id`     | Unique customer ID                         |
| `email_sent_date` | Date when email was sent                   |
| `email_opened`    | 1 = opened, 0 = not opened                 |
| `email_clicked`   | 1 = clicked, 0 = not clicked               |
| `purchase_made`   | 1 = purchase happened, 0 = no purchase     |
| `purchase_amount` | Order value (if purchase happened)         |
| `device_type`     | Mobile / Desktop / Tablet                  |
| `customer_city`   | Customer city                              |
